Jamaican Vomiting Sickness

) The leftmost route on the wall. Steep and cryptic. There are plenty of holds but figuring out which one to use on this steep route takes time and adds to the pump. 7 bolts to a 2 bolt anchor.

(

Do Not Resuscitate

) The route on the right side of the wall. Starts out easy but ends with tiny edges on overhanging rock. Not as good as the other routes on the wall but a worthy outing if you hike up here
